or a creed that you live by?

1148
01:20:52,058 --> 01:20:54,060
Well, personally,

1149
01:20:54,227 --> 01:20:57,939
I like to think about sex and drugs
and rock'n'roll. That's my life.

1150
01:20:58,106 --> 01:21:01,651
If you were to have something written
as your epitaph...

1151
01:21:03,027 --> 01:21:06,072
Here lies David St Hubbins,

1152
01:21:08,199 --> 01:21:10,701
and why not?

1153
01:21:11,577 --> 01:21:15,915
- You feel that sums up your life?
- No. It's the first thing I could think of.

1154
01:21:16,082 --> 01:21:18,084
